Kaijudo: Rise of the Duel Masters - Season 1 - Episode 5 (WEB-DL - 720p)

Kaijudo: Rise of the Duel Masters is an animated action-adventure fantasy series
that tells the story of Raiden "Ray" Pierce-Okamato, a talented 14 year-old
creature tamer, 'whisperer' and duelist who along with his friends Allie
and Gabe, battle the evil forces that are appearing in our world who have come
through the Veil, to wreak havoc. In the world of Duel Masters, other-worldly
creatures, 'kaiju' co-existed with mankind for thousands of years. All was
peaceful for centuries, but now The Veil has begun to tear, and creatures are
coming to Earth with frightening regularity. Mankind's hope rests with those
brave few who can tame the creatures... The Duel Masters!

Produced by Hasbro Studios.

Animated by MOI Animation.
